<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><font face="arial">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Thanks for purchasing your policy with us and welcome to Kingsbridge!</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">When you bought your policy, <b>you told us you were referred by a friend</b>. If you have their permission to do so, <b>please send us the details of the person who referred you</b>. Be sure to include their email address, so that we can send them some vouchers as a thank you.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Unfortunately, we are unable to accept an email where your friend is cc'd. Instead, please make sure their details are included in the body of the email.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Don't forget, <b>you can benefit from our Refer a Friend scheme too</b>. There's no limit to the number of people you can refer and we will send you £50 in online vouchers.</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">For more information, or to refer a friend now, just visit this link: https://www.kingsbridge.co.uk/refer-a-friend/&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Kind regards,</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">{!User.FirstName}</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">Customer Service Team</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</font></div><div style=""><font face="arial">T: 01242 808 740</font></div></div></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>